							<li><b>Date:</b> 11/30</li>						
							<li><b>Time:</b> 10am-6pm</li>
							<li><b>Location:</b> ART lobby</li>
					</div>
					<div id="box2">
						<p>Germany during the Cold War Photography Exhibit</p>
