				</div>
				<div id="backgroundFiller" style="background:white; opacity:.9; width:500px; height:450px; -moz-border-radius: 3px; border: 3px; position:relative; top:20px;"></div>
				<div id="event-info">
					<br></br>

					<div id="imageimageimage">
				<%= image_tag "camera.jpg", :id=>"event-image" %>
					<div id="info"><ul>
						<li><font size="3pt" face="arial" color="black"><b>Date:</font></b> <font color="black"> 11/30</font></li>
						<li><font size="3pt" face="arial" color="black"><b>Time:</font></b> <font color="black"> 10am-6pm</font></font></li>
						<li><font size="3pt" face="arial" color="black"><b>Location:</font></b><font color="black"> ART lobby</font></font></li>
				</ul></div>					
					</div>	
					<ul style="position:relative; top:-100px;">
						<br></br>
						<li><font size="3pt" face="arial" color="black"><b>Description:</font></b> <font color="black">This is an all-day workshop from 10 am - 6 pm. We'll start by learning exposure basics on a DSLR camera,and spend the rest of the day learning how to create amazingly lit photos using only a single flash. We'll
spend a short time looking at how to improve the quality of on-camera flash, then learn the many, many
ways to create creative, beautiful light by taking that flash off the camera.</font></font></li>
					</ul>				
			</div></div>
			<div id="box2-expanded" style="border: 2px solid #000000;">
				<div id="event-title" style="border: 1px solid #000000;">
					<p> Germany during the Cold War Photography Exhibit </p>			
				</div>
				<div id="event-info"></div>
					<div id="event-image">
				<%= image_tag "judo.png" %>
					</div>					
			</div>
			<div id="box3-expanded" style="border: 2px solid #000000;">
				<div id="event-title" style="border: 1px solid #000000;">
					<p> Event 3 title </p>			
				</div>
				<div id="event-info"></div>
					<div id="event-image">
						<%= image_tag "judo.png" %>
					</div>					
			</div>	
	</div>		
